  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>Last updated: December 2025</p>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Amora TeaOnHer</strong> (“the App”)
    handles information when you use it. The App is developed and operated by an
    individual developer (“we”, “us”, or “our”).
  </p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Amora TeaOnHer is a finger training application designed to help users improve
    dexterity and hand activity through simple exercises. User privacy is a core
    principle of the App.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Collection</h2>
  <p>
    The App does <strong>not collect</strong>, store, or process any personal data.
    No information is transmitted from your device to us or to any third parties.
  </p>

  <h2>Permissions</h2>
  <p>
    The App may request permission to send local notifications. These notifications
    are generated and handled entirely on your device and are not used to collect
    or transmit any data.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Storage</h2>
  <p>
    The App does not store user data on external servers and does not use cloud
    storage or backups.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    The App does not use third-party analytics, advertising, tracking, or crash
    reporting services.
  </p>

  <h2>User Identification</h2>
  <p>
    The App does not require account creation, registration, login, or any form of
    user identification.
  </p>

  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children. Since
    no personal data is collected, no data related to users of any age is stored
    or shared.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted
    on this page with an updated revision date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:
    <br>
    <strong>Email:</strong> vibesdeckapp@gmail.com
  </p>

